# Vale packages fetched by `vale sync` (e.g. Google/) are NOT vendored — only our
# own Alethia style and vocab config are committed. Leading-slash anchors match ONLY
# the top-level dirs of styles/ (a bare `*/` is recursive and would also re-ignore
# nested config/ subdirs, which git then can't re-include).
/*/
!/Alethia/
!/config/
